sequenceDiagram
    participant Index as Models Index YAML<br/>data/validated-models-index.yaml
    participant Extractor as model-extractor CLI<br/>(Go, build-time only)
    participant Registry as OCI Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>huggingface.co<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>output/ & data/
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>ubi9-minimal
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>(Consumer)

    Note over Extractor: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation

    Extractor->>Index: Read models index YAML
    Index-->>Extractor: OCI image references

    loop For each model (max 5 concurrent)
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Registry-->>Extractor: OCI manifest (architectures, layers)
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/blobs/{digest}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Registry-->>Extractor: Layer blob (modelcard.md extraction)
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/blobs/{config}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Registry-->>Extractor: Config blob (timestamps, arch)
    end

    Note over Extractor,HF: Enrichment Phase (optional)

    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections/RedHatAI<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>Extractor: Collection list & model IDs

    loop For each model
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model_id}<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details (downloads, likes, tags, license)
        Extractor->>HF: GET /{model_id}/raw/main/README.md<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        HF-->>Extractor: README YAML frontmatter (provider, tasks, languages)
    end

    Extractor->>FS: Write extracted metadata<br/>output/{model-name}/
    Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/models-catalog.yaml
    Extractor->>FS: Write validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/validated-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over Extractor: Flow 3: MCP Server Catalog

    Extractor->>FS: Read MCP server index YAML
    FS-->>Extractor: MCP server definitions

    loop For each MCP server
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{mcp-image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Registry-->>Extractor: MCP image manifest (arch, timestamps)
    end

    Extractor->>FS: Write redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml<br/>data/redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over Container: Build Phase (Konflux/GitHub Actions)

    FS->>Container: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/<br/>Dockerfile.konflux build

    Note over Container,Dashboard: Flow 2: Runtime Data Access

    Container->>Container: CMD ["sleep", "infinity"]
    Dashboard->>Container: Volume mount /app/data/
    Container-->>Dashboard: Catalog YAML files<br/>(models, MCP servers)
